{"id":259076,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/bbc-陈光诚纽约获颁人权奖/","date":"2012-10-25T05:45:42Z","modified":"2012-12-30T14:45:08Z","title":"BBC | 陈光诚纽约获颁人权奖","content":"<p>中国盲人维权活动人士陈光诚获得一个美国人权组织颁发的年度人权奖。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/bbc-%e9%99%88%e5%85%89%e8%af%9a%e7%ba%bd%e7%ba%a6%e8%8e%b7%e9%a2%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%9d%83%e5%a5%96/1351138563_6ed3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-259077\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-259077\" title=\"\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/1351138563_6ed3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/1351138563_6ed3.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/10/1351138563_6ed3-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" /></a></p>\n<p>美国“人权至上”组织星期三（10月24日）在纽约举行年度盛会，并向陈光诚颁发2012人权奖。去年12月曾试图到东师古村探访当时仍被软禁的陈光诚但被阻拦的好莱坞影星贝尔给陈光诚颁奖。</p>\n<p>来源：BBC</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,8779],"tags":[20203,9050,18807,19253,20711,15095]}